desc: This family (PF06439) includes 3-ketoglycoside lyases such as BT2157 (also known as BtOGE2). The metal-coordinating side chains are N134, E164, Q166, Q273; Y190 and H275 are catalytic bases; and K245 activates Y190 as a base. In the tree, BT2157 and other 3-ketoglycoside lyases (from genetic data) are colored green, and endoglucanase THTE_1561 is in red. These family members were taken from MicrobesOnline (using hits to PFam PF06439.11 with 80 bits or higher), clustered at 60% identity to reduce the number of sequences, and aligned using hmmalign.
